  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The incomplete resection rates in polyps from Group 1 (clear margins) versus Group 2 (positive margins).</measure>
    <time_frame>Between 3-6 months</time_frame>
    <description>Define the frequency of free margins versus margins that have dysplasia to the cautery site in snare polypectomy. A free margin is defined as uninvolved or normal mucosa extending to the cautery margin at the polypectomy stalk.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
